 the pouch necessary to combine the items.<br><br>3) Once you have acquired the pouch. Head to the first floor and camp the random rare spawn Commander Zazuzh. He drops the idol you need.<br><br>4) Once you've acquired the idol, go to the second floor and in similiar fashion camp the random rare spawn Commander Zeruzsh. He drops the ring you need.<br><br>5) Then head to the Imperial Guard chamber where you can access the locked teleport to the Emperor's chamber. By killing the Imperial Guards you can spawn 3 named rares all of which drop the last piece you need, the insignia. These are General Kizuhx, Arbiter Korazhk, and Advisor Zekuzh.<br><br>6) Put all 3 items into the pouch and combine. You will receive a Ring of the Shissar.<br><br><br><br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uxiggin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xiggin</A> at: 5/13/02 9:51:01 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucolcannon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Colcannon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/3/02 4:17:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5276.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.bippiboy.com/images/stuff/homesm.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Updated Vex Thal Info - With 10 Shards</span><hr size=1> Being nitpicky here, but the name of the tribe in Dawnshroud is Sambata and not Sambala :)<br><br><br>Ya know... if they were thinking two steps ahead they woulda made the components drop from some of the mobs needed for the twilight armour quests. By doing it that way, there is a good chance the PHs would get quicker and the actual quest mobs would appear with greater freq